snippet.title: F-Zero GX US Commercial
snippet.description:
This is the commercial for F-Zero GX when it came out for the Nintendo Gamecube. This commercial was rarely seen at the time and it's rare to find today. This commercial is very similar to the Japanese version. The only difference between the US and Japanese versions are the different background music and the US one is missing the part that shows connectivity with F-Zero AX.

This game is awesome but HARD! Enjoy.
